hed in Cherry or Black in all sides.";i:26;s:75:"They have a beveled edge perfect to add LED rope lighting below the risers.";i:27;s:38:"Tapered Portable Choral Risers by NPS.";i:28;s:26:"Modular Stages by Caprock.";i:29;s:39:"Box Pleat Skirting for Portable Stages.";i:30;s:54:"TransFold Dual Height Stages w Carpet Deck by Midwest.";i:31;s:61:"TransFold Dual Height Stages w Polypropylene Deck by Midwest.";i:32;s:52:"Tiered Theater Seats Home Theater Seating on Risers.";i:33;s:42:"Everyone loves a night out at the theater.";i:34;s:176:"The big screen the superior sound the comfortable seating the hot buttery popcornit all adds up to a great experience that for the longest time could not be replicated at home.";i:35;s:83:"It is also possible to tune your home theater chair riser as a Helmholtz resonator.";i:36;s:31:"This will take a bit more work.";i:37;s:73:"You will need to first figure out what bass frequencies you need to tame.";i:38;s:85:"Then you can make inner chambers inside the riser that will impact those frequencies.";i:39;s:64:"The port size or holes in the front of the riser panel are also.";i:40;s:67:"Posts about theater chair riser written by mccabestheaterandliving.";i:41;s:97:"I get this question several times a day and generally people dont realize how many options there.";i:42;s:74:"Mar 28 2015 - Explore Suzie Lews board Home theater - risers on Pinterest.";i:43;s:58:"See more ideas about home theater home home theater rooms.";i:44;s:96:"First off you CAN add a built-in riser to The Flex HR and Turbo XL700 by Octane Theater Seating.";i:45;s:93:"Its a great feature and is much less expensive then building a full riser in your media room.";i:46;s:86:"Lets do just a general estimate of room depth that will allow for two rows of seating.";i:47;s:65:"Comfortable viewing for the first row is about 8 from the screen.";i:48;s:79:"Oct 22 2019 - Riser We bought some theater chairs from our local Movie theater.";i:49;s:41:"We bought enough chairs to make two rows.";i:50;s:46:"I wanted to build a riser for the back row so.";i:51;s:146:"If you can only do an 8 riser youll need the bottom of the screen material to be at least 38 off the riser level with typical home theater chairs.";i:52;s:91:"For rooms with a tall ceiling you can get that great stadium seating effect with 15 risers.";i:53;s:79:"This gives you the standard step height of 7 ½ for each step up to your riser.";i:54;s:19:"14 Picture Gallery.";i:55;s:34:"Home Theater Chair Riser Pictures.";i:56;s:75:"Home Theater Riser Height And Optimization Guide Audio Advice Audio Advice.";i:57;s:50:"Theater Seating Riser Mccabe S Theater And Living.";i:58;s:62:"Home Theater Seating Bluffton Sc Advanced Integrated Controls.";i:59;s:66:"The Ovation Home Theater Chair By Palliser Custom Theater Seating.";i:60;s:68:"These theater seat risers have recliner features and a sturdy build.";}}